Relationship to FFmpeg
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This product is a pure-Java library that invokes the external `ffmpeg` and
`ffprobe` command-line programs as separate subprocesses. It does NOT link
against, statically or dynamically embed, or otherwise incorporate the FFmpeg
libraries (libavcodec, libavformat, etc.) or any FFmpeg source code. FFmpeg is
neither bundled with nor distributed as part of this product.

Consequently, this product is not a derivative work of FFmpeg and is licensed
